Step 1. edit the variables in the Makefile.
Step 2. make sure you at least look at the variables in the Makefile.
run 'make runonce' to demo the indicator applet
run 'make install' to install to $FILE_DIR

DEPENDENCIES
python-gtk2

GET LIST OF MAKE COMMANDS
make

TO INSTALL
make install (includes autostart_on)

TO UNINSTALL (included autostart_off)
make uninstall

AUTOSTART (with gnome-session)
make autostart_on
make autostart_off

TO ADD HOSTS
edit $FILE_DIR/config.xml

SET CONFIG TO DEFAULTS
make configinstall

Try without installing:
make runonce
